{"tid":2334341,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大規模接種疫苗，會令病毒變種，英國就係咁出事","createTime":"2020-12-21T06:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T06:47:55.000Z","uid":134093,"like":10,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"387775207020166b3334347cc588ac97818f74fb","tid":2334341,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:15:59.000Z","msg":"英國新病毒株傳染力高左7成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港都唔會例外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次香港第四波好大機會係由接種左疫苗人士傳入<br />\n<br />\n再諗下有乜人可以自由出入香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫雞群組啲雞全部非法入境，呢班雞仲要全部打過晒疫苗先嚟<br />\n<br />\n先唔講隻疫苗有冇效，但打左都係會傳染仲有機會變種<br />\n<br />\n所以可以預視到香港將來會大爆發<br />\n<br />\n當香港大規模強制性打疫苗之後，肯定大把人會當無事發生，除罩周街去，加上病毒變種，好快會大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係一發不可收拾果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfaf5b3510626d6980f8d8a324a3810e85b3dcfc","tid":2334341,"uid":134093,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:18:07.000Z","msg":"英國打左第一日就變種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1abe2c21da1c0828ee1a03e2e6e21710ede441","tid":2334341,"uid":220942,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:18:34.000Z","msg":"英國佬出口術<br />\n講到好噢嚴重咁<br />\n等多啲人去打苗啫"},{"pid":"b879ab72c15adf40122bf1ac63ab027d957e2e01","tid":2334341,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"邊有咁快啊<br />\n數碼暴龍都唔係話進化就進化啦"},{"pid":"80975a52b4dfeb49db92abd152351d8371ac6fe7","tid":2334341,"uid":79174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:22:05.000Z","msg":"生化危機2021<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9cc6e4674ff22483917f298ba4ae737c4f51fd4","tid":2334341,"uid":189847,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pi