20-12-21T06:18:34.000Z","msg":"英國佬出口術<br />\n講到好噢嚴重咁<br />\n等多啲人去打苗啫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:27:55.000Z","msg":"民主國家冇得用依招.<br />\n你呃9 人民. 下次選舉一定輸梗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:34:24.000Z","msg":"出口術 不等於 呃9人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a331d9a8432b9fa344d16b5860f84ee694270f78","tid":2334341,"uid":253608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9eaf1af6281a0f990cb62f2b18745707a4fce2a","tid":2334341,"uid":276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:29:59.000Z","msg":"隻變種病毒株10月首次發現，不如你睇多次新聞先作！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4314b8a45a493a4f3db3e5b97b6c94c3a12a8d01","tid":2334341,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f9eaf1af6281a0f990cb62f2b18745707a4fce2a","tid":2334341,"uid":276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:29:59.000Z","msg":"隻變種病毒株10月首次發現，不如你睇多次新聞先作！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:41:19.000Z","msg":"係9月發現<br />\n<br />\n新變種病毒首次於今年9月被發現。<br />\n<br />\n11月份的統計顯示四分之一的倫敦確診案例來自該變種病毒。到12月中旬，這一數字已接近三分之二。<br />\n這三件事融合在一起，這引起了人們高度關注：<br />\n<br />\n1. 正在迅速取代其他新冠病毒版本。<br />\n2. 重要的是，它能部分影響新冠病毒突變。<br />\n3. 一些突變已在實驗室中檢驗出來，突變增強病毒感染細胞的能力。<br />\n<br />\n唔敢講一定關事，但病毒會喺康復者身上變種<br />\n<br />\n直到現在病毒仍然不斷地嘗試不同的變化來感染人類。之前就發生過類似情況，G614變異毒株讓許多人擔心傳染力增強。<br />\n大規模疫苗接種也會給新冠病毒帶來新的壓力，因為病毒需要改變才能感染那些接種過疫苗的人。"},{"pid":"77e396267962c932371b7cb382e19aeb91069f30","tid":2334341,"uid":276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:46:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[quote]隻變種病毒株10月首次發現，不如你睇多次新聞先作！</blockquote>係9月發現<br />\n<br />\n新變種病毒首次於今年9月被發現。<br />\n<br />\n唔使打咁長，你呢句：英國打左第一日就變種<br />\n解釋下<br />\n補充：12月先打疫苗"},{"pid":"702cefdd5d31dcc4339aebd296e50dad14002476","tid":2334341,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfaf5b3510626d6980f8d8a324a3810e85b3dcfc","tid":2334341,"uid":134093,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:18:07.000Z","msg":"英國打左第一日就變種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:47:52.000Z","msg":"Fake News<br />\n<br />\n變種病毒9月已發現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19f46d43a63c8ed68b5ed94b4459252a33d3776","tid":2334341,"uid":276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:47:55.000Z","msg":"叫雞群組啲雞全部非法入境，呢班雞仲要全部打過晒疫苗先嚟<br />\n<br />\n樓主屋企人做雞定雞頭？<br />\n<br />\n如果你本來想學術討論，就唔撚7好落啲咁ON 9嘅論點先啦"}]}